profile:
We offer aluminum railing made right here in the Okanagan. Choose from a variety of styles and patterns – many styles from pickets to topless glass systems in your choice of color.
Our decking products include 60 ml vinyl decking, approved seamless liquid coating (super-deck), non-skid commercial flooring, CGSB approved spray-on roof membrane, and garage floor coatings – all available in a wide assortment of colors and styles. 
We absolutely guarantee competitive estimates/quotes and the highest quality of workmanship.
